    <item>
      <title>达利欧称中国领导人面临“不惜一切代价”的时刻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/dalio-says-china-s-leaders-face-whatever-it-takes-moment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁投资者雷·达利欧 (Ray Dalio) 表示，如果北京的决策者能够兑现“远超”承诺的举措，中国的市场刺激举措将成为世界第二大经济体的历史性转折点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/dalio-says-china-s-leaders-face-whatever-it-takes-moment</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 17:49:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯将前往佐治亚州和北卡罗来纳州调查海伦飓风造成的损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/harris-to-visit-georgia-north-carolina-to-survey-helene-damage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯将前往佐治亚州和北卡罗来纳州，访问两个遭受飓风海伦袭击的州，这两个州也是11月与共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普角逐的关键战场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/harris-to-visit-georgia-north-carolina-to-survey-helene-damage</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 17:43:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
