      <title>美国财政部呼吁中国货币互换保持透明度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/us-treasury-calls-for-transparency-on-china-s-currency-swaps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部一名高级官员指出，中国的外汇互换额度缺乏透明度，并敦促国际货币基金组织谨慎对待将其简单地纳入发展中国家官方储备的计算中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/us-treasury-calls-for-transparency-on-china-s-currency-swaps</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 17:36:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗导弹袭击以色列 以色列迅速承诺予以报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/israel-says-iran-has-launched-missiles-in-direct-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗周二向以色列发射了约 200 枚弹道导弹，这是中东两个对手之间激烈但短暂的升级，有可能引发新一轮袭击，以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡誓言要进行报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/israel-says-iran-has-launched-missiles-in-direct-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 16:43:11 GMT</pubDate>
